::Shredder::

Shredder nods, looking from Mantella to Magmatron.

"It sounds good," he says to Mantella. He turns to Magmatron.

"Very well," he says to him, strapping the device to his arm. He looks at 
Magmatron.

"Lead the way," he says, reffering to Magmatron's base.
